<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV88">
<l>veḷḷaivēlai veṟpunāṭṭi veḷḷeyiṟṟa rāvaḷā</l>
<l>yaḷḷalākka ṭaintavaṉṟa ruvaraikko rāmaiyā</l>
<l>yuḷḷanōykaḷ tīrmaruntu vāṉavarkka ḷittavem</l>
<l>vaḷḷalārai yaṉṟimaṟṟor teyvamnāṉma tippaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>On the day the white ocean was churned so that it became muddy,</l>
<l>setting up a mountain, stirring [it with] a white-fanged snake,</l>
<l>[You] became a tortoise for the sake of the mountain [in] difficulty,</l>
<l>and gave to the celestials the nectar that ends the[ir] pains.</l>
<l rend="indent">Would I value a god other than our generous Lord [who did that]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
